    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Bless</strong> (Level 1 Enchantment)</p><p>You bless up to three creatures of your choice within range. Whenever a target makes an attack roll or a saving throw before the spell ends, the target can roll a d4 and add the number rolled to the attack roll or saving throw.</p><p><em>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level above 1st.</em></p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (A sprinkling of holy water.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> 30 feet | <strong>Duration:</strong> Up to 1 minute (Concentration)</p><p><em>Classes: Cleric, Paladin</em></p>",
